verbose_text: Because our data indicated that GDF15 increased Kv2.1 protein synthesis and prevented its degradation, we first tried to determine whether the Akt / mTOR pathway, which has been reported to affect protein synthesis and CGN mutation [XREF_BIBR, XREF_BIBR], was activated by GDF15.
